id=hidepid
name=HidePID - PID + App Hiding
version=v2.0.0
versionCode=2
author=hidepid
description=Kernel-level PID + App hiding via filldir hook, with WebUI management. Features: hide PIDs from /proc, hide apps from /data/data, auto-scan running processes, module self-hiding. Manage via WebUI or: echo <pid> > /proc/.pidmap
